===================================================================
RCS file: /usr/cvs/ports/editors/emacs/Makefile,v
retrieving revision 1.26
diff -u -r1.26 Makefile
--- Makefile	1996/11/19 13:14:40	1.26
+++ Makefile	1997/05/20 10:25:09	1.28
@@ -20,5 +20,11 @@
